column8: This is estimated using DHIS2 vmmc cases and world bank population data 2015-2019.

From 2020 on as indicated by DHIS2 data and PEPFAR 2020 Country Operational Plan the <15 yrs circ cases should decline dramatically. The probability derived from 2020-2022 data is 0.0008 using the same estimation method.
